 classes for JDBC-based data access in Spring Boot applications. It configures data sources, JDBC templates, transaction managers, database initialization, health checks, connection pool metrics, and Docker Compose/Testcontainers connection details.\",\nmetadata/org.testcontainers/testcontainers/1.17.6/reachability-metadata.json:5:        \"typeReached\": \"org.testcontainers.shaded.com.github.dockerjava.core.DefaultInvocationBuilder\"\nmetadata/org.testcontainers/testcontainers/1.17.6/reachability-metadata.json:7:      \"type\": \"com.github.dockerjava.api.command.AsyncDockerCmd\"\nmetadata/org.testcontainers/testcontainers/1.17.6/reachability-metadata.json:13:      \"type\": \"com.github.dockerjava.api.command.CreateConfigResponse\",\nmetadata/org.testcontainers/testcontainers/1.17.6/reachability-metadata.json:21:      \"type\": \"com.github.dockerjava.api.command.CreateContainerResponse\",\nmetadata/org.testcontainers/testcontainers/1.17.6/reachability-metadata.json:27:        \"typeReached\": \"org.testcontainers.shaded.com.github.dockerjava.core.exec.CreateContainerCmdExec\"\nmetadata/org.testcontainers/testcontainers/1.17.6/reachability-metadata.json:29:      \"type\": \"com.github.dockerjava.api.command.CreateContainerResponse\",\nmetadata/org.testcontainers/testcontainers/1.17.6/reachability-metadata.json:53:      \"type\": \"com.github.dockerjava.api.command.CreateImageResponse\",\nmetadata/org.testcontainers/testcontainers/1.17.6/reachability-metadata.json:61:      \"type\": \"com.github.dockerjava.api.command.CreateNetworkResponse\",\nmetadata/org.testcontainers/testcontainers/1.17.6/reachability-metadata.json:69:      \"type\": \"com.github.dockerjava.api.command.CreateSecretResponse\",\nmetadata/org.testcontainers/testcontainers/1.17.6/reachability-metadata.json:77:      \"type\": \"com.github.dockerjava.api.command.CreateServiceResponse\",\nmetadata/org.testcontainers/testcontainers/1.17.6/reachability-metadata.json:85:      \"type\": \"com.github.dock