brary runtime dependencies. So, do we have \\\"concrete evidence\\\" that the extra dependency is necessary? If we recommend using Docker, then yes, it seems crucial for writing clean JUnit tests. Plus, the existing TCK already utilizes Testcontainers, which adds to its relevance.\"}]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "{\n  \"action\": \"advisory_preparation\",\n  \"summary\": \"Apache Pulsar Java client is primarily exercised through producer/consumer/reader operations against a running Pulsar broker; the artifact is otherwise self-contained, but meaningful end-to-end coverage needs a standalone broker.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [\n    {\n      \"kind\": \"dependency\",\n      \"coordinate\": \"org.testcontainers:testcontainers:1.19.8\",\n      \"scope\": \"testImplementation\",\n      \"reason\": \"Needed by generated JUnit tests to start and manage a disposable standalone Pulsar broker for producer/consumer coverage.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"kind\": \"docker_image\",\n      \"image\": \"apachepulsar/pulsar:4.2.1\",\n      \"slug\": \"pulsar\",\n      \"reason\": \"Official Pulsar image matching the requested client version; documentation uses standalone Pulsar on ports 6650 and 8080 for client examples.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"Start a standalone broker with command `bin/pulsar standalone`, expose broker port `6650` and HTTP/admin port `8080`, wait for readiness before creating the client, and build clients with `PulsarClient.builder().serviceUrl(\\\"pulsar://<host>:<mapped-6650>\\\").build()`. Use unique topic names under `persistent://public/default/` and close producers, consumers, readers, and clients to avoid thread/resource leaks.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The standalone Pulsar container can be slow to start and may be resource-heavy in native-image test runs.\",\n    \"Without the broker setup, tests can still cover builders, schemas, authentication factories, and message-id utilities, but they will miss the core producer/consumer path that defines normal client usage.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_05a1b3a78bafa6be016a28fa64e7c48190bb4ebbe5749bb93b\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 797, "output": 2436, "cacheRead": 45056, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 48289, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1781070385085, "responseId": "resp_05a1b3a78bafa6be016a28fa31ad148190bb1d081afbd89c36"}}
